descriptions.nowplaying: Shows the information from the current music
descriptions.play: Play a song from an URL or searching it
descriptions.spotify: See the current Spotify music information of an user
descriptions.queue: Removes a music from the queue
descriptions.stop: Stops the current music and terminates the active queue.
descriptions.lastfm: See an user's profile on Last.fm
descriptions.playnow: Immediately plays a track, ignoring the current one and/or the queue
